Symbol.Script_3D:
! Fire Dept Inlet Connection
IF gs_detlevel_3D_m = -1 THEN gs_detlevel_3D_m = 2 ! Detailed IF gs_detlevel_3D = `Откл.` THEN gs_detlevel_3D_m = 0 IF gs_detlevel_3D = `Простой` THEN gs_detlevel_3D_m = 1 ENDIF
IF gs_detlevel_3D_m = 0 THEN END
res = 24 ! Detailed IF gs_detlevel_3D_m = 1 THEN res = 8 ! Simple
IF useSysMat THEN MainBoxMaterial = sMat MATERIAL MainBoxMaterial PEN gs_cont_pen RESOL res
unID = 1
! --- FIRE DEPARTMENT INLET CONNECTION --- !
IF gs_detlevel_3D_m = 2 THEN ! Detailed
IF objType = 1 THEN ! 2-Way Flush FD Connection Outlet Body GOSUB 100 ENDIF
IF objType = 2 THEN ! 2-Way Flush FD Inlet Connection Plate GOSUB 200 ENDIF
IF objType = 3 THEN ! 3-Way Flush FD Connection Outlet Body GOSUB 300 ENDIF
IF objType = 4 THEN ! 3-Way Flush FD Inlet Connection Plate GOSUB 400 ENDIF
IF objType = 5 OR objType = 7 THEN ! 2-Way Projecting FD Inlet Connection IF objType = 5 THEN fthk = MIN(0.15*A, ConWidth_1/2) cx = fthk/3+ConWidth_1/2 ELSE fthk = 0.05*A cx = fthk+ConWidth_1/2 ENDIF
REVOLVE 2,360, 1+2+4+16+32, 0, B/2, 2, fthk,B/2, 2
GROUP "Main" REVOLVE 2,360, 1+2+4+16+32, fthk, 1.1 * ConWidth_1/2, 2, cx+0.0001, 1.1 * ConWidth_1/2, 2 ENDGROUP
GROUP "Branch" pathL = A/SQR(2) ADDx cx ROTx 90 CUTPLANE DEL 1 ROTz 45 REVOLVE 4,360, 1+2+4+16+32, 0, 1.1 * ConWidth_1/2, 2, pathL-0.1*A, 1.1 * ConWidth_1/2, 2, pathL-0.1*A, 1.2 * ConWidth_1/2, 2, pathL, 1.2 * ConWidth_1/2, 2 HOTSPOT pathL,0,0, unID: unID=unID+1 CUTEND DEL 1
ROTx 90 CUTPLANE 180 DEL 1 ROTz -45 REVOLVE 4,360, 1+2+4+16+32, 0, 1.1 * ConWidth_1/2, 2, pathL-0.1*A, 1.1 * ConWidth_1/2, 2, pathL-0.1*A, 1.2 * ConWidth_1/2, 2, pathL, 1.2 * ConWidth_1/2, 2 HOTSPOT pathL,0,0, unID: unID=unID+1 CUTEND DEL 2 ENDGROUP
PLACEGROUP ADDGROUP("Main", "Branch") KILLGROUP "Main" KILLGROUP "Branch" ENDIF
IF objType = 6 OR objType = 8 THEN ! 3-Way Projecting FD Inlet Connection IF objType = 6 THEN fthk = MIN(0.15*A, ConWidth_1/2) cx = fthk/3+ConWidth_1/2 ELSE fthk = 0.05*A cx = fthk+ConWidth_1/2 ENDIF
REVOLVE 2,360, 1+2+4+16+32, 0, B/2, 2, fthk,B/2, 2 REVOLVE 4,360, 1+2+4+16+32, fthk, 1.1 * ConWidth_1/2, 2, 0.9*A, 1.1 * ConWidth_1/2, 2, 0.9*A, 1.2 * ConWidth_1/2, 2, A, 1.2 * ConWidth_1/2, 2 HOTSPOT A,0,0, unID: unID=unID+1
ROTy 90 CUTPOLYA 2,1,0, 0,0,913, 1.1 * ConWidth_1/2, 360,4013 DEL 1
pathL = A/SQR(2) ADDx cx ROTz 45 REVOLVE 4,360, 1+2+4+16+32, 0, 1.1 * ConWidth_1/2, 2, pathL-0.1*A, 1.1 * ConWidth_1/2, 2, pathL-0.1*A, 1.2 * ConWidth_1/2, 2, pathL, 1.2 * ConWidth_1/2, 2 HOTSPOT pathL,0,0, unID: unID=unID+1 ROTz -90 REVOLVE 4,360, 1+2+4+16+32, 0, 1.1 * ConWidth_1/2, 2, pathL-0.1*A, 1.1 * ConWidth_1/2, 2, pathL-0.1*A, 1.2 * ConWidth_1/2, 2, pathL, 1.2 * ConWidth_1/2, 2 HOTSPOT pathL,0,0, unID: unID=unID+1 DEL 3 CUTEND ENDIF
IF objType = 9 THEN ! Single Flush FD Inlet Connection REVOLVE 6,360, 1+2+4+16+32, 0, B/2, 2, 0.1*A, B/2, 2, 0.1*A, 1.2 * ConWidth_1/2, 2, 0.7*A, 1.2 * ConWidth_1/2, 2, 0.7*A, 1.5 * ConWidth_1/2, 2, A, 1.5 * ConWidth_1/2, 2 HOTSPOT A,0,0, unID: unID=unID+1 ENDIF ENDIF
IF gs_detlevel_3D_m = 1 THEN ! Simple
IF objType = 1 THEN ! 2-Way Flush FD Connection Outlet Body GOSUB 100 ENDIF
IF objType = 2 THEN ! 2-Way Flush FD Inlet Connection Plate GOSUB 200 ENDIF
IF objType = 3 THEN ! 3-Way Flush FD Connection Outlet Body GOSUB 300 ENDIF
IF objType = 4 THEN ! 3-Way Flush FD Inlet Connection Plate GOSUB 400 ENDIF
IF objType = 5 OR objType = 7 THEN ! 2-Way Projecting FD Inlet Connection IF objType = 5 THEN fthk = 0.15*A cx = fthk/3+ConWidth_1/2 ELSE fthk = 0.05*A cx = fthk+ConWidth_1/2 ENDIF
REVOLVE 2,360, 1+2+4+16+32, 0, B/2, 2, fthk,B/2, 2
GROUP "Main2" REVOLVE 2,360, 1+2+4+16+32, fthk, 1.1 * ConWidth_1/2, 2, cx+0.0001, 1.1 * ConWidth_1/2, 2 ENDGROUP
GROUP "Branch2" pathL = A/SQR(2) ADDx cx ROTx 90 CUTPLANE DEL 1 ROTz 45 REVOLVE 2,360, 1+2+4+16+32, 0, 1.1 * ConWidth_1/2, 2, pathL, 1.1 * ConWidth_1/2, 2 CUTEND DEL 1
ROTx 90 CUTPLANE 180 DEL 1 ROTz -45 REVOLVE 2,360, 1+2+4+16+32, 0, 1.1 * ConWidth_1/2, 2, pathL, 1.1 * ConWidth_1/2, 2 CUTEND DEL 2 ENDGROUP
PLACEGROUP ADDGROUP("Main2", "Branch2") KILLGROUP "Main2" KILLGROUP "Branch2" ENDIF
IF objType = 6 OR objType = 8 THEN ! 3-Way Projecting FD Inlet Connection IF objType = 6 THEN fthk = 0.15*A cx = fthk/3+ConWidth_1/2 ELSE fthk = 0.05*A cx = fthk+ConWidth_1/2 ENDIF
REVOLVE 2,360, 1+2+4+16+32, 0, B/2, 2, fthk,B/2, 2 REVOLVE 2,360, 1+2+4+16+32, fthk, 1.1 * ConWidth_1/2, 2, A, 1.1 * ConWidth_1/2, 2
ROTy 90 CUTPOLYA 2,1,0, 0,0,913, 1.1 * ConWidth_1/2, 360,4013 DEL 1
pathL = A/SQR(2) ADDx cx ROTz 45 REVOLVE 2,360, 1+2+4+16+32, 0, 1.1 * ConWidth_1/2, 2, pathL, 1.1 * ConWidth_1/2, 2 ROTz -90 REVOLVE 2,360, 1+2+4+16+32, 0, 1.1 * ConWidth_1/2, 2, pathL, 1.1 * ConWidth_1/2, 2 DEL 3 CUTEND ENDIF
IF objType = 9 THEN ! Single Flush FD Inlet Connection REVOLVE 4,360, 1+2+4+16+32, 0, B/2, 2, 0.1*A, B/2, 2, 0.1*A, 1.5 * ConWidth_1/2, 2, A, 1.5 * ConWidth_1/2, 2 ENDIF ENDIF
DEL TOP RESOL res
! --- CONNECTIONS --- !
CALL "MEP_m_ConnectionsMEP_4" PARAMETERS SetProgram = SetProgram, ui_current_con = ui_current_con, MEP_NumberConnections = MEP_NumberConnections, MEP_NumConnectionData = gs_Connections, gs_AddConnections = gs_AddConnections, cShow3D = 1, gs_ConMat = MainBoxMaterial, MEP_InsShow = 0, MEP_cline_show_3D = 0, gs_cont_pen = gs_cont_pen, ConPosX_1=ConPosX_1, ConPosY_1=ConPosY_1, ConPosZ_1=ConPosZ_1, ConLength_1=ConLength_1, ConEdit_1 = ConEdit_1, ConPosX_2=ConPosX_2, ConPosY_2=ConPosY_2, ConPosZ_2=ConPosZ_2, ConLength_2=ConLength_2, ConEdit_2 = ConEdit_2, ConPosX_3=ConPosX_3, ConPosY_3=ConPosY_3, ConPosZ_3=ConPosZ_3, ConLength_3=ConLength_3, ConEdit_3 = ConEdit_3, ConPosX_4=ConPosX_4, ConPosY_4=ConPosY_4, ConPosZ_4=ConPosZ_4, ConLength_4=ConLength_4, ConEdit_4 = ConEdit_4 END
! 2-Way Flush FD Connection Outlet Body 100: bR = ZZYZX/2 cx = 1.05 * bR RR = B/2-bR
HOTSPOT cx,0,0, unID: unID=unID+1
GROUP "Inlet_1" ROTy 90 CYLIND cx, bR DEL 1 ENDGROUP
GROUP "Arch_1" ADDx cx+RR ROTy -90 REVOLVE 2,180, 1+2+4+8, 0,RR,901, bR,360,4001 DEL 2 ENDGROUP
PLACEGROUP ADDGROUP("Inlet_1", "Arch_1") KILLGROUP "Inlet_1" KILLGROUP "Arch_1"
ADD cx+RR, RR, 0 ROTy 90 PRISM_ 2,A-cx-RR, 0,0,978, bR,360,4078 DEL 2 ADD cx+RR,-RR, 0 ROTy 90 PRISM_ 2,A-cx-RR, 0,0,978, bR,360,4078 DEL 2 RETURN
! 2-Way Flush FD Inlet Connection Plate 200: thk=MAX(0.005, 0.05*A) ROTy 90 PRISM 4, thk, -ZZYZX/2, -B/2, ZZYZX/2, -B/2, ZZYZX/2, B/2, -ZZYZX/2, B/2
HOTSPOT -ZZYZX/2, -B/2, 0, unID: unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT ZZYZX/2, -B/2, 0, unID: unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT ZZYZX/2, B/2, 0, unID: unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT -ZZYZX/2, B/2, 0, unID: unID=unID+1 DEL 1
ADD thk, ConPosY_1,0 ROTy 90 CYLIND A-thk, ConWidth_1/2 HOTSPOT 0,0,A-thk, unID: unID=unID+1 DEL 2
ADD thk, ConPosY_2,0 ROTy 90 CYLIND A-thk, ConWidth_2/2 HOTSPOT 0,0,A-thk, unID: unID=unID+1 DEL 2 RETURN
! 3-Way Flush FD Connection Outlet Body
300: bR = ZZYZX/2 cx = 1.05 * bR RR = B/2-2*bR
! HOTSPOT cx,0,0, unID: unID=unID+1
L=B-2*(RR+bR) ADD cx,-L/2,0 ROTx -90 PRISM_ 2,L, 0,0,974, bR,360,4074 DEL 2
ADDx cx ROTz 180 ROTx 90 ARMC bR,bR, cx, 0,0,90 DEL 3
IF A-cx > bR THEN ADDx cx ROTx 90 ARMC bR,bR, A-cx, 0,0,90 DEL 2 ENDIF
FOR i=1 TO 2 ADD cx+RR,B/2-bR-RR,0 ROTy -90 REVOLVE 2,90, 1+2+4+8, 0,RR,901, bR,360,4001 DEL 2 ADD cx+RR,B/2-bR, 0 ROTy 90 PRISM_ 2,A-cx-RR, 0,0,978, bR,360,4078 DEL 2
MULy -1 NEXT i DEL 2
RETURN
! 3-Way Flush FD Inlet Connection Plate 400: thk=MAX(0.005, 0.05*A) ROTy 90 PRISM 4, thk, -ZZYZX/2, -B/2, ZZYZX/2, -B/2, ZZYZX/2, B/2, -ZZYZX/2, B/2
HOTSPOT -ZZYZX/2, -B/2, 0, unID: unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT ZZYZX/2, -B/2, 0, unID: unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT ZZYZX/2, B/2, 0, unID: unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT -ZZYZX/2, B/2, 0, unID: unID=unID+1 DEL 1
ADD thk, ConPosY_1,0 ROTy 90 CYLIND A-thk, ConWidth_1/2 HOTSPOT 0,0,A-thk, unID: unID=unID+1 DEL 2
ADD thk, ConPosY_2,0 ROTy 90 CYLIND A-thk, ConWidth_2/2 HOTSPOT 0,0,A-thk, unID: unID=unID+1 DEL 2
ADD thk, ConPosY_3,0 ROTy 90 CYLIND A-thk, ConWidth_3/2 HOTSPOT 0,0,A-thk, unID: unID=unID+1 DEL 2 RETURN
